<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Wheel on Loving life and Coding</title><link>https://qybit.gitee.io/tags/wheel/</link><description>Recent content in Wheel on Loving life and Coding</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 Nov 2020 18:28:45 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://qybit.gitee.io/tags/wheel/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Trie树</title><link>https://qybit.gitee.io/2020/11/26/trie%E6%A0%91/</link><pubDate>Thu, 26 Nov 2020 18:28:45 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://qybit.gitee.io/2020/11/26/trie%E6%A0%91/</guid><description>&lt;p>Trie树是一种特殊的数据结构，它常用于在数据中检索字符串。也可以叫做字典树和前缀树等等。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>手动实现LinkedList</title><link>https://qybit.gitee.io/2020/11/25/%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0linkedlist/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 Nov 2020 15:44:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://qybit.gitee.io/2020/11/25/%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0linkedlist/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="前言">前言&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>链表是与线性表相对应的一种特殊的数据结构，它的各个节点在物理内存上可以是连续的也可以是不连续的，逻辑上链表是连续的。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>优点&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>增删效率高&lt;/li>
&lt;li>适合经常更改的应用场景&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>缺点&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>查询效率很低&lt;/li>
&lt;li>不适合经常查询的应用场景&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>优缺点是相当于线性表而言！&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>